{"tid":1586354,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解次次都會第一時間屌打錯人、送頭呢？","createTime":"2019-09-22T02:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:15:38.000Z","uid":161430,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8565c8c0fa8b50905bad126b04cc99015b023a63","tid":1586354,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:19:24.000Z","msg":"因為其實呢d人根本自己就信唔過前線，又有階級之分，<br />\n咁咪會好易睇低人、多疑囉。<br />\n<br />\n好似你返工，心入面覺得個新黎個同事廢，<br />\n就算佢冇做錯野，有少少事 你都好易誤會佢。<br />\n<br />\n一個教畜唔信學生，學生冇做錯野，教畜都會成日挑剔佢。<br />\n<br />\n連登有一小部分人就係咁，往往未有咩事，就屌左前線先。<br />\n<br />\n例如一個行動有幾千、幾萬人參與，<br />\n只係一有一兩個人被捕，仲要未知佢真街坊定前線、和理非，<br />\n總之果d人就會屌定先: 「屌又送頭 有冇腦」。<br />\n<br />\n好似琴晚咁，根本未確認咩事，又會講定一定係打錯人先。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢d人個腦入面，一早預設好前線一定衰硬，<br />\n唔信任係default設定，<br />\n於是佢地只不過係等緊幾時有事發生，一有事就可以blame得，<br />\n以證明佢既default諗法係岩。<br />\n<br />\n唔該呢堆人反省下自己用咩眼光睇前線，<br />\n有冇真正用一個非從屬，大家平起平坐、能力一樣既態度，<br />\n真正信任前線呢？"},{"pid":"7e0140f9490e4ae68cb7d316c72bafeeb5eb9191","tid":1586354,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:20:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b95fcda954d44ec3981d4e5638feb2acbac8727","tid":1586354,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"成班五毛浪費緊大家時間 唔好同佢地鳩"},{"pid":"9cf25868392fa87b18e6e66dccd7a6b178539254","tid":1586354,"uid":4838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"琴日成班p牌出黎係咁屌打錯人<br />\n正如早排見到國歌成功團結港人就係咁屌唱歌左膠無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩人我諗大家心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb194c00ce545a25f8055d07eaad1709e9f4c6d9","tid":1586354,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0140f9490e4ae68cb7d316c72bafeeb5eb9191","tid":1586354,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:20:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人真係有團結<br />\n<br />\n但成日好易講又送頭 唉打錯人 果堆<br />\n只係口頭上講團結 以為自己團結左<br />\n實際上太重階級觀念<br />\n由上而下咁低一堆同自己並肩作戰既前線<br />\n真係當左自己係指揮官咁<br />\n<br />\n冇一種平起平坐既觀念<br />\n就會好易第一時間走去judge人做錯野"},{"pid":"2f9d1a583f0e602ef1b80b147f591c19a17543b3","tid":1586354,"uid":157396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"深藍屋企人睇TVB....<br />\n<br />\n聽到火滾...報個阿伯講到好似殺佢咁...<br />\n<br />\n個程度講到仲嚴重過721, 821..<br />\n<br />\n已經估到對家一定狂放大呢件事...<br />\n<br />\n希望記者星期一唔理POPO記者會講呢件事講到有幾嚴重..<br />\n<br />\n唔該問返佢地721, 831同琴日邊日嚴重D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有義士比人斬到行唔返路..係咪黃絲比人斬就可以當睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n藍絲比人打到流血(仲可以企到起身)就可以講到黑衫要謀殺佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6e1f59bd47aef3ced14d21e5dc005997551e15","tid":1586354,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb9e3077e5ec5b81e71b54181d418d201ece77b4","tid":1586354,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"冷氣佬都唔知憑咩覺得自己高人一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725aeb301cd525c5c4737afa5d5fc9415c322fec","tid":1586354,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"連我老母睇到都話抵死打得好<br />\n點解反而冷氣軍師就咁多疑呢"},{"pid":"7e73b85d2c1c0cac9f6ca43d6728e1f9ea40054c","tid":1586354,"uid":4731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"唔好畀人spin<br />\n今日拉咗幾多FA<br />\n將軍澳十歲細路都拉呀"},{"pid":"5a370d09e739dd2a13fcc5c46b970a06ccc2958e","tid":1586354,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"其實警察都好有人<br />\n下次不如試下唔好自衛由得警察拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb235b2302d8721296d31ef97a733208bc266d3","tid":1586354,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a370d09e739dd2a13fcc5c46b970a06ccc2958e","tid":1586354,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"其實警察都好有人<br />\n下次不如試下唔好自衛由得警察拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"愛與和平穿透坦克了"},{"pid":"68617ca1a003c0d361958945d155461320985448","tid":1586354,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"725aeb301cd525c5c4737afa5d5fc9415c322fec","tid":1586354,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"連我老母睇到都話抵死打得好<br />\n點解反而冷氣軍師就咁多疑呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:36:38.000Z","msg":"主要係階級觀念太重 仲係覺得自己比較高等<br />\n<br />\n如果一個人真係有信任另一個同伴<br />\n都會包括埋信任人地都有正常智商同能力<br />\n同自己冇太大分別<br />\n<br />\n但部分冷氣軍師或者提倡人人平等既左膠，<br />\n往往最易有階級之分 (例如起大台等行為已經係)<br />\n而且最容易訴諸權威，<br />\n例如一篇文章，如果寫文人自稱為律師、行內人士，<br />\n呢班冷氣軍師或左膠會傾向認為篇文好有道理。<br />\n<br />\n另外藍絲都好有呢種特質，<br />\n所以佢地先會咁相信官方授權既執法者，<br />\n例如警察等人先係做緊正確既事。<br />\n<br />\n前線往往冇呢種權威，階級上唔係高級既人，<br />\n冷氣軍師同左膠就最易會先入為主，睇低前線各種既行動"},{"pid":"5e732045220dbbd3616c36a346037f98c4c48688","tid":1586354,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9e3077e5ec5b81e71b54181d418d201ece77b4","tid":1586354,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"冷氣佬都唔知憑咩覺得自己高人一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"上帝視角全知型鍵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05782b3d07030d42ca619a807cec3e7789a03d6","tid":1586354,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"講得岩"},{"pid":"5c1d32bd8b549a756a85767bb68e7dc58776721c","tid":1586354,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"冷氣佬 on9 一睇就知和理非都未做過 仲有好撚多五毛"},{"pid":"228f1c79aee550821db3948da05b64e5b6d72084","tid":1586354,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"連登咩人都有<br />\n打緊仗開po屌前線既人，到底係唔係同路人<br />\n有保留"},{"pid":"30ee95ad50794bd9b3f776b64fd521089dd6cfed","tid":1586354,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"如果真係去除左階級觀念，做到平起平坐，<br />\n並且相信大家都係香港人，係共同體<br />\n<br />\n你一定會信任前線，而即使前線做野錯，<br />\n你第一時間都會想比建議佢地，同埋維護佢地，<br />\n而唔會係未確認發生咩事，就屌定佢地on9 做錯野<br />\n「又送頭」「打錯人喇屌」"},{"pid":"788ea416c4de6e95fe01e4e399e8a9925c787753","tid":1586354,"uid":81375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd96116b911db735b65911b733c45f54de9e2ce9","tid":1586354,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"因為嗰班係鬼，分化撚，冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港</span>"},{"pid":"2cae628b1967e4caf47ad87e22a2060dceeb1bc2","tid":1586354,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf25868392fa87b18e6e66dccd7a6b178539254","tid":1586354,"uid":4838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"琴日成班p牌出黎係咁屌打錯人<br />\n正如早排見到國歌成功團結港人就係咁屌唱歌左膠無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩人我諗大家心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"P牌就算尻數啦，都唔知係咪自己友"},{"pid":"541c4ba23dfaf43d3ab5acd8429a93c2796acda2","tid":1586354,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"喂,  同一道理啫<br />\n<br />\n你又憑咩去覺得  <br />\n出 post 話前線打錯人送頭既人係「和理非」   而唔係敵人既打手 or 一毛有心搞亂  ?<br />\n<br />\n你地啲 logic 又係有啲怪  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c